aic2024.user

Class StructureInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • aic2024.user.StructureInfo

  • public class StructureInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Class with the information of a given structure at a given timestamp. Note that the values are immutable, and thus they don't update over time. For example if a structure receives damage, any StructureInfo associated to that structure will not change.
